content:
The authentication pattern for Android apps integrated with Marketing Cloud Engagement is changing to stay compliant with requirements for Google Firebase Cloud Messaging. To send push notifications to Android devices after this date, admins can upload the Service Account JSON file for each active Android app before June 1, 2024.

Where: This change applies to all Marketing Cloud Engagement editions.

When: Complete all uploads by June 1, 2024.

How: To upload Service Account JSON files, go to the Administration tab in MobilePush.
title: Upcoming Authentication Change for Android Apps in Marketing Cloud Engagement
